resourceAbstractObject.default: Data from the 'Seismic hazard' (ALEA): Acquisition, processing and provision of observations and databases used to define seismogenic sources in seismic hazard models. This observatory is part of the Montpellier Research Observatory of Environment (OSU OREME, oreme.org). It is labelized in the framework of Action Transverse Sismicité Epos-France. It consists in different observing tasks: FACT ; FMHEX.
